  <title>
    <phrase lang="de">Vertikal Spiegeln</phrase>
    <phrase lang='en'>Flip Vertically</phrase>
    <phrase lang='fr'>Miroir Vertical</phrase>
    <phrase lang="zh_CN">水平(垂直)翻转</phrase>
  </title>

  <indexterm lang="en">
    <primary>Layer</primary>
    <secondary>Flip vertically</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="de">
    <primary>Ebene</primary>
    <secondary>drehen</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="fr">
    <primary>Calque</primary>
    <secondary>Miroir vertical</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang="fr">
    <primary>Miroir vertical (calque)</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <para lang='en'>   
    "Flip Vertically" reverses the active layer top-to-bottom.  This 
    command leaves layer dimensions unchanged; neither causes any 
    degradation of pixel data in the layer.
  </para>
  <para lang="de">
    Mit diesem Kommando können Sie die aktive Ebene vertikal, also entlang der
    y-Achse, spiegeln.
  </para>
  <para lang='fr'>
    "Miroir Vertical" retourne le calque actif de haut en bas. Cette 
    commande laisse les dimensions et les pixels du calque inchangés.
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">   
    “水平翻转”将图层从左到右反向，而“垂直翻转”将它从上到下反向。它们都保持图层尺寸不变，也不会使图层任何像素数据丢失。
  </para>


  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase lang="en">Activate Dialog</phrase>
      <phrase lang="cs">Aktivace dialogu</phrase>
      <phrase lang="de">Aufruf des Kommandos</phrase>
      <phrase lang="fr">Appel de la commande</phrase>
      <phrase lang="zh_CN">开启对话框</phrase>
    </title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para lang='en'>
          These commands can be accessed from an image menubar as
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>L</accel>ayer</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransform</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>Flip <accel>V</accel>ertically</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang="de">
          Das Kommando kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden:
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>E</accel>bene</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransformation</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem><accel>V</accel>ertikal spiegeln</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang='fr'>
          On accède à ces commandes à partir de la barre de menu de l'image
          par
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu><accel>C</accel>alque</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu><accel>T</accel>ransformer</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>Miroir <accel>V</accel>ertical</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
        <para lang="zh_CN">
          这些命令在图像菜单的
          <menuchoice>
            <guimenu>图层</guimenu>
            <guisubmenu>变换</guisubmenu>
            <guimenuitem>垂直翻转</guimenuitem>
          </menuchoice>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
